{"tid":1072723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"講真 梁天琦判無罪唔好咁開心住","createTime":"2019-03-22T07:53:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-22T12:55:33.000Z","uid":220779,"like":60,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f3b2b64e1b43b078be2d72f573e34c7f52877f45","tid":1072723,"uid":220779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T07:53:11.000Z","msg":"今次陪審團判無罪嘅係「於砵蘭街參與暴動」<br />\n<br />\n之前仲有項罪名係「於亞皆老街參與暴動」<br />\n被陪審團判左有罪 一樣要坐6年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最好笑嘅係 今次判無罪就個個話香港法治有救<br />\n明明之前梁天琦判暴動有罪就個個話香港法治已死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"113abae3dd11e02c94baf94503f72e47492e1514","tid":1072723,"uid":29270,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T07:54:27.000Z","msg":"明明人地仲坐緊監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a2b9ee503475ecbd6c47e297e89d5f0021cb0da","tid":1072723,"uid":64374,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T07:54:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e6760bf8770e5fbc751f39bbc4d3a65a8b63cd4","tid":1072723,"uid":140769,"like":6,"dislike":33,"score":-27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T07:55:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"743e80add827926a1219d7617b31c63adaaedf82","tid":1072723,"uid":220779,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T08:06:43.000Z","msg":"判有罪嘅係陪審團<br />\n判無罪嘅又係陪審團<br />\n咁究竟jury system係咪廢"},{"pid":"8e44911e1b677f79d119f2478d5c3a498c29dd8b","tid":1072723,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T08:07:47.000Z","msg":"如果無陪審團制度，就99%入梗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d51e88e6a5d5634755f81545af8aa7d0c22020d6","tid":1072723,"uid":135274,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score